description: Erection of a basement and part 5, part 6 storey building behind a retained facade (199-205 Richmond Road) comprising: 97 residential units (42x1, 22x2, 24x3, 8x4 and 1x5 bed units); 2436 sqm (GEA) of business floorspace (class B1); 370 sqm of flexible floorspace within retail (class A1), cafe / restaurant (class A3) and business uses (class B1); 227 sqm of flexible floorspace within retail (class A1) and cafe / restaurant uses (class A3); together with associated enabling works, car and cycle parking and landscaping.
